Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 2022.11.21
1. Introduction
Welcome to Muushig ("we," "us," or "our"). We are committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application Muushig (the "App").
By accessing or using the App, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
2. Information We Collect
2.1.
Information You Provide:
We may collect information that you voluntarily provide when using the App, such as your name, email address, username, and other information you submit through the App.
2.2.
Automatically Collected Information:
We may collect certain information automatically, including your device's unique identifier, IP address, mobile device operating system, and usage data.
3. How We Use Your Information
We may use the information we collect for various purposes, including:
• Providing and improving the App's features and functionality.
• Responding to user inquiries and support requests.
• Sending you updates, notifications, and promotional materials.
• Monitoring and analyzing usage patterns and trends.
• Complying with legal obligations.
4. Disclosure of Your Information
We may share your information with:
• Third-party service providers that assist us with App operation and maintenance.
• Law enforcement or regulatory authorities when required by law.
• Other users, as part of the App's social features (e.g., multiplayer functionality).
5. Data Deletion
You have the right to request the deletion of your personal information held by us. To do so, please refer to the "Contact Us" section (Section 9) of this Privacy Policy for our contact information. We will make reasonable efforts to delete your data, subject to any legal or regulatory obligations that may require us to retain certain information.
6. Data Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, please be aware that no data transmission over the internet is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee the security of your data.
7. Children's Privacy
Our App is not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children under 13. If we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will promptly delete it.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically for changes. Your continued use of the App after changes to the Privacy Policy constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or wish to request data deletion, please contact us at below:
• Email: contact@muushig.mn
• Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/muushig.chandmani.tech
• Messenger:
https://m.me/muushig.chandmani.tech
